'''Aɣyul''' (illa mad as ittinin '''Aɣyyul''', ar ittaddr f "yay") iga yan ɣ imudar lli ɛicnin d ufgan ar ittaws i middn lli zdaɣnin ɣ udrar ard ittawi ikccuḍn yawid aman ɣ wanu.

Aɣyul yan umudr ɣ wanaw n Ayyis, iga amuder ssegman medden, yili yan wanaw yaḍen ittidiren g tagant d isaffen d tnẓruft n tfriqt d asya d imerdal-nnes. aɣyul yamu g wanaw n iyyesan id-emm yan ikfer, yumu g winna issuḍuḍen, ig asmun n umdan aha, ar as ittasey tiɣawsiwin-nnes. ar ttinin i wmeẓẓan n uɣyul asnus.

==Tasnazɣuṛt : ==
Assaɣ n uɣyyul s tutlayt tarumit (Talatint) igat "Asinus", g tmaziɣt tlla taguri irwasn taguri ad, as tt igan d "Asnus"; Asnus g tmaziɣt igat umẓẓay n uɣyyul nɣ iwis n uɣyyul.

